{
  "texts": [
    "All prompts were used as input for ChatGPT 4.0 (OpenAI, 2024) with the resulting lesson plan output saved to a text file.",
    "Each prompt (P.1-P.5) was input 10 times to capture non-deterministic output arising from the temperature parameter.",
    "Each prompt and prompt iteration occurred on new chats to ensure no influence of the prior prompt on the output.",
    "All text files were labeled by prompt.",
    "For example, P1.1 represented the first time Prompt 1 was entered and P5.5 represented the fifth time Prompt 5 was entered."
  ]
}